			<br>
			<li>SSH to 130.49.222.93
			<li>cd to (or create) your working directory
			<li>cvs -d /var/lib/cvsroot checkout virtualclassroom - to checkout the entire project
			<br>
			<br>
			Download the CVS manual <a href="./cvs_manual.pdf>here</a> for details about all commands
